# codeplug-tool edits

Read [`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md) first. For git, plans, and docs see [`.cursor/skills/`](../skills/).

**Critical rules:** [vendor-boundaries.mdc](vendor-boundaries.mdc), [no-wire-stash-roundtrip.mdc](no-wire-stash-roundtrip.mdc), and [format-agnostic-docs.mdc](format-agnostic-docs.mdc). When editing related files, if you notice violations — even outside your current task — **flag them to the user as a high concern** before or alongside your main work. Do not silently ignore, copy the pattern, or defer without mention. Do not attempt to fix if it's outside the original instruction.

## Vendor boundaries

Internal model, store, mutations, validation, and CRUD UI are **vendor-neutral** — UUID FKs, no wire-name resolution, no radio profile constants or member-count caps. See [vendor-boundaries.mdc](vendor-boundaries.mdc) and [AGENTS.md — Vendor boundaries](../../AGENTS.md#vendor-boundaries).

## SPA (`src/`)

- React + TypeScript under `src/`; Vite bundles for GitHub Pages (`base: '/codeplug-tool/'`).
- Routing via `react-router` HashRouter.
- Build info via Vite `define` — see [version-number skill](../skills/version-number/SKILL.md).

## Channel map

- UI: `src/components/ChannelMap/ChannelMap.tsx`
- Parsing and geometry: `src/lib/csv.ts`, `src/lib/channels.ts`, `src/lib/geo.ts`
- Route: `/#/map` via `src/routes/Map.tsx`
- CPS CSV parsing (import/export adapters): match columns by **header name**, not index.
- Zone hulls use the same coordinate filters as channel markers (`Use Location`, skip `0,0`).
- A channel may appear in multiple zones — each zone hull includes shared members independently.
- Mapbox tokens: `localStorage` only; never commit tokens or require a server.

## Scope

- GitHub Pages deploy is release-triggered — see `docs/build/README.md`.
- Do not add committed sample codeplugs; use gitignored `sample-exports/` for local CSVs.
